## SavedObjectsServiceSetup.setClientFactoryProvider property

Set the default [factory provider](./opensearch-dashboards.savedobjectsclientfactoryprovider.md) for creating Saved Objects clients. Only one provider can be set, subsequent calls to this method will fail.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
setClientFactoryProvider: (clientFactoryProvider: SavedObjectsClientFactoryProvider) => void;
```
